@page
@model HealthConnect.Pages.AboutModel
@{
    Layout = "_Header";
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<div class="about-container">
    <div class="about">
        <h1 class="about-title">Welcome to Health Connect</h1>

        <p class="about-paragraph">
            <strong>Health Connect</strong> is your all-in-one digital healthcare solution designed to bring the hospital to your fingertips. Whether you need medical advice, want to consult with a doctor, order medicines, or simply read expert-written health articles — we’ve got you covered.
        </p>

        <h2 class="about-subtitle">Consult Doctors from Anywhere</h2>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
            Say goodbye to waiting rooms. With Health Connect, you can instantly <strong>book online video consultations</strong> with experienced and certified doctors. Whether you're facing a minor ailment or need follow-up care, our platform allows you to connect with healthcare professionals from the comfort of your home, office, or while traveling.
        </p>

        <p class="about-paragraph">
            Prefer meeting in person? We also offer the option to <strong>book on-site doctor consultations</strong>. Just choose your doctor, select the time slot, and confirm your appointment — it’s that simple.
        </p>

        <h2 class="about-subtitle">Chat with Doctors — Absolutely Free</h2>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
            For general queries and quick health tips, we provide a <strong>free chat service</strong> that connects users with qualified doctors. Get medical guidance, prescription clarifications, or lifestyle advice without any charges.
        </p>

        <h2 class="about-subtitle">Easy Online Pharmacy Access</h2>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
            Once your doctor consultation is complete, you’ll receive a digital prescription. With just a few clicks, you can <strong>order your prescribed medicines</strong> from our in-platform pharmacy and have them delivered to your doorstep — safe, fast, and secure.
        </p>

        <h2 class="about-subtitle">Stay Informed with Health Blogs</h2>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
            Explore our wide range of <strong>health blogs and articles</strong> written by professionals. From fitness tips and nutrition advice to updates on medical innovations and disease prevention — our blogs keep you informed and empowered.
        </p>

        <h2 class="about-subtitle">Why Choose Health Connect?</h2>
        <ul class="about-list">
            <li>✔ Convenient video and on-site consultations</li>
            <li>✔ Free doctor chat for quick queries</li>
            <li>✔ Safe and reliable online medicine delivery</li>
            <li>✔ Insightful and informative health content</li>
            <li>✔ Secure, user-friendly platform accessible 24/7</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="about-paragraph">
            Our mission is to make healthcare more accessible, affordable, and personalized. With Health Connect, expert medical care is always just a click away.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
